Package: cellrangercheck
Title: Parse and QC Cell Ranger count/multi Outputs Across GEM Wells
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Shihan", "Li", email = "shihanli1992@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Point the package at a set of Cell Ranger run directories (each a
    separate GEM reaction) and parse 'cellranger count' and 'cellranger multi'
    outputs into one tidy, comparable table of pipeline quality-control metrics.
    Reads metrics_summary.csv (wide count and long multi formats), reads the
    filtered/raw feature-barcode HDF5 matrices to derive barcode-rank knee
    points and per-cell UMI/gene distributions, flags wells against configurable
    thresholds, and renders a side-by-side HTML report.
